31:["$","p","26",{"children":["So using the satoshi math, 210,000×5,000,000,000×2=2,100,000,000,000,000 sats. In other words we still arrive at 21 million.",["$","br","1",{"children":"$undefined"}],"But the",["$","strong","3",{"children":" true supply"}]," is: 2,099,999,997,690,000 sats. Why is this slightly less than 21 million?"]}]
32:["$","p","27",{"children":["Because of the way the >>= operator works in code. ",["$","br","1",{"children":"$undefined"}],["$","br","2",{"children":"$undefined"}],"Here's the crux of the magic: ",["$","br","4",{"children":"$undefined"}],"nSubsidy >>= halvings"]}]
33:["$","p","28",{"children":["What this effectively means is that the subsidy is calculated by taking the math-floor of the max-subsidy divided by 2^halvings.",["$","br","1",{"children":"$undefined"}],["$","br","2",{"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","3",{"className":"katex","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"katex-mathml","children":["$","math",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML","children":["$","semantics",null,{"children":[["$","mrow","0",{"children":[["$","mtext","0",{"children":"nSubsidy"}],["$","mo","1",{"children":"="}],["$","mrow","2",{"children":[["$","mo","0",{"fence":"true","children":"⌊"}],["$","mfrac","1",{"children":[["$","mtext","0",{"children":"nSubsidy"}],["$","msup","1",{"children":[["$","mn","0",{"children":"2"}],["$","mtext","1",{"children":"halvings"}]]}]]}],["$","mo","2",{"fence":"true","children":"⌋"}]]}]]}],["$","annotation","1",{"encoding":"application/x-tex","children":"\\text{nSubsidy} = \\left\\lfloor \\frac{\\text{nSubsidy}}{2^{\\text{halvings}}} \\right\\rfloor"}]]}]}]}],["$","span","1",{"className":"katex-html","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"base","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"strut","style":{"height":"0.8889em","verticalAlign":"-0.1944em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"mord text","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord","children":"nSubsidy"}]}],["$","span","2",{"className":"mspace","style":{"marginRight":"0.2778em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","3",{"className":"mrel","children":"="}],["$","span","4",{"className":"mspace","style":{"marginRight":"0.2778em"},"children":"$undefined"}]]}],["$","span","1",{"className":"base","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"strut","style":{"height":"1.8em","verticalAlign":"-0.65em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"minner","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"mopen delimcenter","style":{"top":"0em"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"delimsizing size2","children":"⌊"}]}],["$","span","1",{"className":"mord","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"mopen nulldelimiter","children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"mfrac","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"vlist-t vlist-t2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"vlist-r","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"vlist","style":{"height":"0.9322em"},"children":[["$","span","0",{"style":{"top":"-2.6426em"},"children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"pstrut","style":{"height":"3em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"mord mtight","children":"2"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"msupsub","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"vlist-t","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"vlist-r","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"vlist","style":{"height":"0.782em"},"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"top":"-2.786em","marginRight":"0.0714em"},"children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"pstrut","style":{"height":"2.5em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord text mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":"halvings"}]}]}]}]]}]}]}]}]}]]}]}]}]]}],["$","span","1",{"style":{"top":"-3.23em"},"children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"pstrut","style":{"height":"3em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"frac-line","style":{"borderBottomWidth":"0.04em"},"children":"$undefined"}]]}],["$","span","2",{"style":{"top":"-3.4461em"},"children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"pstrut","style":{"height":"3em"},"children":"$undefined"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord text mtight","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"mord mtight","children":"nSubsidy"}]}]}]}]]}]]}],["$","span","1",{"className":"vlist-s","children":"​"}]]}],["$","span","1",{"className":"vlist-r","children":["$","span",null,{"className":"vlist","style":{"height":"0.3574em"},"children":["$","span",null,{"children":"$undefined"}]}]}]]}]}],["$","span","2",{"className":"mclose nulldelimiter","children":"$undefined"}]]}],["$","span","2",{"className":"mclose delimcenter","style":{"top":"0em"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"delimsizing size2","children":"⌋"}]}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","br","4",{"children":"$undefined"}],["$","br","5",{"children":"$undefined"}],"What this is saying in plain English: ",["$","strong","7",{"children":"take the max block subsidy (50 coins), and then divide it by 2 raised to the number of halvings that have occurred, and round down to the nearest integer."}]," This means that some of the satoshis get lost. The fractions of satoshis after epoch 10 get clipped.","$L43","This was a trade-off that Satoshi made, that reveals his genius engineering."]}]
